/eminem-janet-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/eminem-janet-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/eminem-janet-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2025 年歌曲作者名人堂入选者名单已经揭晓，其中不包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆 (Eminem)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janet-jackson">珍妮·杰克逊 (Janet Jackson)</a>等提名艺人。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">埃米纳姆 – 《The Death of Slim Shady (Coup De Grâce)》评论：精心制作的歌曲和空洞的挑衅</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（1 月 22 日），歌曲作者名人堂<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eminem-janet-jackson-and-boy-george-among-2025-songwriters-hall-of-fame-nominees-3812190">在 11 月宣布提名者</a>后<a href="https://www.songhall.org/news/view/songwriters_hall_of_fame_announces_2025_inductees">，公布了 2025 届的入围者</a>。今年入选歌曲作者名人堂的有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-clinton">乔治·克林顿</a>、杜比兄弟、阿什利·戈尔利、罗德尼·杰金斯、迈克·洛夫和托尼·麦考利。</p><p> 11 月份获得提名但未能晋级的艺人包括阿姆 (Eminem)、珍妮·杰克逊 (Janet Jackson)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boy-george">乔治男孩 (Boy George)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特 (Alanis Morissette)</a> 、谢丽尔·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">克劳 (Sheryl Crow)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nwa">NWA</a> 、布莱恩·亚当斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-adams">Bryan Adams)</a>等。共有 26 名艺术家获得提名，其中只有 6 名入选。</p><p>这六位入选者将于 6 月在纽约市举行的 2025 年入职及颁奖晚会上接受表彰。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812191" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812191" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812191" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/eminem-janet-jackson-boy-george@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-