XLP乙烯基按压，其中包括一张折叠海报和一本具有八页小册子的2xCD。这张专辑是由洛杉矶艺术总监克里斯蒂娜·黄（Christina Huang）委托和设计的。它具有Röyksopp的Tflorencerue Electric Tour的摄影作品，由Stian Andersen和Suie Le创作。</p><p>除了即将发行的专辑的宣布之外，Röyksopp还分享了美国新巡回演出日期的细节。 <a href="https://royksopp.com/true-electric/?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAaZGFIQm2eL4rkGjHPH1vIEZ85mSTc0xsASce6JY_RxjjjNv44BWwmQlK6k_aem_7pur-Rpa-4hUhPrHrdGFcw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>注册的人将提供预售。预售将于周四（1月30日）当地时间上午10点开始。通用门票销售将于周五（1月31日）当地时间上午10点开始。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Froyksopp-tickets%2Fartist%2F2940768" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票，并在下面查看巡回演出的完整列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3831194" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831194" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831194" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="RöyksoppTrue Electric Tour海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/True-Electric-Tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831194" class="wp-caption-text"> RöyksoppTrue Electric Tour海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>Röyksopp的“ True Electric DJ” 2025 Tour Dates是：</strong></h2><p><strong>一月</strong><br /><strong>24  - 米兰米兰基地</strong><br /><st